history:
Step 1: Open All trails app
Step 2: Go to the search bar
Step 3: search for trails near 98104 zip code
Step 4: Click on the first search result
Step 5: Click on the Filters icon at the top right corner of the screen
Step 6: Set the trails distance up to 20 miles
Step 7: Click on the close icon at the top left corner of the screen
Step 8: Swipe up to view more filters
Step 9: Select the Difficulty level as Moderate
Step 10: Click on the See 55 trails Option at the bottom right corner of the screen
instruction: Open All trails app, search for trails near 98104 and sort by distance Up to 20 miles then set the difficulty filter to moderate
